Run the main.py file which will open a window allowing you to enter your username and password to register.
The password would be entered using a camera which will be stored in a text file for confirmation later on.
Once registered a person can easily login using their username and password.

The windows or GUI is created using Tkinter and Python.
The rest of the code is also in Python .
Libraries used :- 

	   	OpenCV
			Numpy

Used Concepts of Convex Hull, Haar like Features and simple file read and write Concepts.
